OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be bright with sunny intervals
OL,7,Fand a few showers. Overnight there
OL,8,Fwill be variable amounts of cloud with
OL,9,Fclear spells but also a few more
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAny early showers soon dying
OL,13,Fout. Then the rest of the day will be
OL,14,Fdry with sunny spells, just the odd
OL,15,Fshower over Argyll.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry,
OL,18,Fbright and warm on Sunday. Mainly dry,
OL,19,Fbright and very warm on Monday,
OL,20,Fperhaps the odd shower. Cloudier on
OL,21,FTuesday with a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
